com.pb.locationintelligence.exception

Class SdkException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.pb.locationintelligence.exception.SdkException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SdkException
extends Exception
    This class represents the Error Response of the Java SDK. There can be two types of error, one propagating from Location Intelligence APIs and other which is internal to SDK. Check errorResponseType to get the type of the error.

        public SdkException.ErrorResponseType getErrorResponseType()

        INTERNAL indicates errors internal to SDK.
